{"type": "article", "id": 2778, "title": "Twig&Leaf teas茶叶包装", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-11T07:50:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232542dTjqYIaLH71eyW56.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t出生于新西兰的设计师 Lillian Cutts 一直在墨尔本从事设计创作工作，除了设计一些个性印刷制品和独立出版物外，Lillian Cutts 有一套名为“ Twig&amp;Leaf teas ”的茶叶包装设计极具特色，管状外形，红、橙、绿、黄、棕以及紫 5 中颜色的包装用来区分不同的口味，且可以循环使用。此外，Lillian Cutts 还推出了同一系列的两套茶具套装。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325409xieRvB0lEtFHgrW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232541Nuon9lx78ZJgQLBv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232541MsYCcay7fS0QGnrH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232542XN7Dayui8AjRkfQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}